at-wrexham-bonus-version-of-new-album-3751422">宣布了即将发行的专辑的奖金版本，其中包括他们在雷克瑟姆举行的2023年大型演出中的现场曲目</a>。您可以<a href="https://uk.kingsofleonshop.com/products/can-we-please-have-fun-wrexham-live-edition-2cd-can-we-please-have-fun-wrexham-live-edition-dual-colour-cassette-signed-art-card" target="_blank" rel="noopener">找到更多并在这里购买</a>。</p><p>他们还将在今年晚些时候踏上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-further-2024-uk-and-ireland-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3591919">英国/爱尔兰</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-announce-2024-world-tour-dates-in-london-and-north-america-3591521">北美巡回演出的日期</a>，包括在伦敦的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST Hyde Park 2024举行</a>的标题表演。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/kings-of-leon-tickets/artist/862453?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHUuy3%3AiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处找到任何剩余的门票（英国/爱尔兰）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caleb-followill-on-why-he-didnt-want-sex-on-fire-to-be-on-only-by-the-night-3754088">Caleb Post Clostill谈到了为什么他不希望“只有在夜晚”出现</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
